276
00:17:30,998 --> 00:17:35,598
Mungkin ponsel dengan sejarah panggilan masuk.

277
00:17:36,898 --> 00:17:39,297
Tn. Sugimoto, yang pergi ke kamar kecil

278
00:17:39,298 --> 00:17:41,497
tepat sebelum tiba di Stasiun Sumita Barat,

279
00:17:41,498 --> 00:17:43,597
